            . I was coming along about a dozen yards from the shop, and saw the prisoner snatch the stockings; I followed and saw him drop them - I am sure he is the man.</p>

               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going home when the gentleman collared me - I am innocent.</p>
